column1: 64:variant;'2018-12-10 00:00:00';'v4.10';'The mutation effect description for truncating mutations in ZRSR2 is: ZRSR2 truncating mutations result in several forms of C-terminally truncated protein. column1: 124:variant;'2018-12-10 00:00:00';'v4.10';'The mutation effect description for truncating mutations in ZRSR2 is: ZRSR2 truncating mutations result in several forms of C-terminally truncated protein.
